; : 161 1379 1775 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1379 M 
-0.200 0 (           Throwing an exception from within a signal handler should be)A 
; : 161 1424 1825 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
