-0.200 0 (         [Greg Colvin:])A 
; : 161 1604 1775 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1604 M 
-0.200 0 (           The C standard allows a signal handler to call signal\(\), and)A 
; : 161 1649 1400 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
