-0.200 0 (             subsequent enumerator in the same enumeration, its type is the)A 
; : 161 2369 1800 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2369 M 
-0.200 0 (             type of its defining expression \(where the default defining)A 
; : 161 2414 1850 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2414 M 
