; : 161 2549 1700 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2549 M 
-0.200 0 (          2\) Give enumerations an "interim" underlying type which is)A 
; : 161 2594 1875 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2594 M 
-0.200 0 (             recomputed after each enumerator, and use that underlying type)A 
; : 161 2639 1200 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2639 M 
-0.200 0 (             in subsequent defining expressions.)A 
; : 161 2729 1825 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2729 M 
