-0.200 0 ( Description:)A 
; : 161 749 675 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 749 M 
-0.200 0 (         [N1053 issue 6.58])A 
; : 161 794 300 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 794 M 
-0.200 0 ( Resolution:)A 
; : 161 839 1750 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 839 M 
-0.200 0 (         Using declarations only affect the visibility of declarations)A 
; : 161 884 1950 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 884 M 
-0.200 0 (         occurring before the using declaration itself; they do not affect the)A 
; : 161 929 1900 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 929 M 
-0.200 0 (         visibility of subsequent declarations with the same name.  However,)A 
; : 161 974 1875 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 974 M 
-0.200 0 (         partial specializations of class templates are found by looking up)A 
; : 161 1019 1700 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1019 M 
-0.200 0 (         the primary class template and then considering all partial)A 
; : 161 1064 1925 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1064 M 
-0.200 0 (         specializations of that template.  So if a using declaration names a)A 
; : 161 1109 1875 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1109 M 
-0.200 0 (         class template, subsequent partial specializations are effectively)A 
; : 161 1154 1900 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1154 M 
-0.200 0 (         visible because the primary template is visible.  The working paper)A 
; : 161 1199 1575 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1199 M 
-0.200 0 (         should make this clear, and should include an example.)A 
; : 161 1244 300 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1244 M 
-0.200 0 ( Resolution:)A 
; : 161 1289 700 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
