-0.200 0 ( Description:)A 
; : 161 1964 875 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1964 M 
-0.200 0 (         [John Spicer, core 7399:]:)A 
; : 161 2009 1700 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2009 M 
-0.200 0 (         Can a template that is only declared \(and not defined\) in a)A 
; : 161 2054 1175 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2054 M 
-0.200 0 (         translation unit be declared "export"?)A 
; : 161 2144 525 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2144 M 
-0.200 0 (         The WP says:)A 
; : 161 2189 1775 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2189 M 
-0.200 0 (         "A non-inline template function or static data member template)A 
; : 161 2234 1750 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2234 M 
-0.200 0 (          is called an exported template if its definition is preceded)A 
; : 161 2279 1725 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2279 M 
-0.200 0 (          by the keyword export or if it has been previously declared)A 
; : 161 2324 1625 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2324 M 
-0.200 0 (          using the keyword export in the same translation unit.")A 
; : 161 2414 1775 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2414 M 
-0.200 0 (         This does not make it clear whether an exported declaration is)A 
; : 161 2459 1550 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2459 M 
-0.200 0 (         ill-formed or whether the "export" is simply ignored.)A 
; : 161 2549 850 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2549 M 
-0.200 0 (         [Erwin Unruh, core-7407:])A 
; : 161 2594 1025 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2594 M 
-0.200 0 (         We have five possible solutions:)A 
; : 161 2639 1125 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2639 M 
-0.200 0 (         1: Allow export only on definitions.)A 
; : 161 2684 1725 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2684 M 
-0.200 0 (         2: Allow export only on entities defined in that translation)A 
; : 161 2729 425 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2729 M 
-0.200 0 (            unit.)A 
; : 161 2774 1725 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2774 M 
-0.200 0 (         3: Allow export on declarations but without semantics if not)A 
; : 161 2819 925 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2819 M 
-0.200 0 (            followed by a definition.)A 
; : 161 2864 1825 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2864 M 
-0.200 0 (         4: Allow export on declarations with the semantic that this will)A 
; : 161 2909 900 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2909 M 
-0.200 0 (            be an exported template.)A 
; : 161 2954 1775 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2954 M 
-0.200 0 (         5: Require export on all declarations of an exported template.)A 
; : 161 2999 700 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 2999 M 
-0.200 0 ( Requestor:      John Spicer)A 
; : 161 3044 1025 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
