-0.200 0 (           called.)A 
; : 161 1604 1775 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1604 M 
-0.200 0 (           To clarify my reasoning: the calling of the base subobject's)A 
; : 161 1649 1675 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1649 M 
